<description></description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There's something special about having one corner of your home that exists purely for slowing down with a good book.</p>

<h2>The essentials</h2>A comfortable chair, soft lighting, a small side table for your tea, and a blanket you can't resist wrapping up in.

<p>Add a few personal touches: a plant, a stack of your favourite reads, and a candle that makes the space feel like a retreat.</p>

<p>You don't need a big house or a fancy budget, just a little corner you'll look forward to coming back to.</p>]]></content:encoded>
