<item>
<title><![CDATA[Sustainable Fashion: Building a Capsule Closet]]></title>
<link>https://example.com/?p=107</link>
<pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://example.com/?p=107</guid>
<description></description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A capsule wardrobe changed the way I shop. Fewer, better pieces that all work together, chosen with care instead of impulse.</p>

<h2>Start with what you love</h2>Look at the clothes you actually wear and notice the patterns. Those favourites are the foundation of your capsule.

<p>Choose natural fabrics, neutral tones, and timeless shapes. When everything coordinates, getting dressed becomes calm instead of chaotic.</p>

<p>Sustainable style isn't about perfection. It's about buying less and wearing it longer.</p>]]></content:encoded>
